{"id": "pos048", "name": "Cam_Dash_702_11_14", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Car_Moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "That was close... Almost got recognized again...\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Thank you, Mr. Asakura. Excuse me for all the ruckus...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Ummm... Mr. Asakura?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO said the bar is located in Quadrant II...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "You... do know the directions, right?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos4503"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah!?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma... I finally found you.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... I...!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Ah! You don't have to be so anxious! Please hear me out. This is the only opportunity I have to properly talk to you...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": ".......\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I'm sorry... This is all my fault. I'm the one responsible for everything. It's only natural that you decided to run away.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "That night, when your sister and I had the big argument... You heard all of it, didn't you?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... Just a little bit...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Is that so... Then I'm about to tell you everything now. Everything we... no, everything I did to you.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Everything...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "That's right. Maybe you'll come to despise me after hearing what I'm about to say, and I wouldn't mind it one bit. I had this coming...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... And this is how we managed to bring you back.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "So this body...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Yes. In reality, this is not your body.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... I... Regarding what I've been able to recall... the memories about my childhood with my sister, those are indeed real. Yet some conflicting images are mixed among these memories...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Yes. This is the exact reason why. In theory, there are two sets of memories existing in your brain right now... I'm sorry. You can despise me all you want; I deserve it.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "I can understand... the emotions you two felt and why you two so desperately wanted to bring me back. So...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No, I'm not done yet. I still have some things... some things I need to tell you. Not even Helena knows about the thing I'm going to tell you next...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "In all honesty, this experiment should've succeeded quite easily. We ended up failing so many times... because of me\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I tampered with your memory copy because back then, I really, really didn't want you to remember... what happened that night...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... The night where you got really drunk and did some things to me... right?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... So you remember? That's right. No matter what I tried, I just couldn't properly control the memory parameters. That was what caused everything to go haywire, all because I was too scared at the possibility of not returning to the simple, happy life we previously had.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Even now, when I look at what I became back then, and what I'm doing now saying all this crap, I feel nothing but disgust toward myself.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah, you didn't actually \"hurt\" me in any way. You collapsed almost immediately after that since you were very drunk...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "That's not the point... My feelings toward you back then, those shouldn't have existed in the first place.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... Yes.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "All I desire right now is for you two sisters to be happy... I mean that wholeheartedly. Please believe me.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah... I...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "We're home. Let's get inside first.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Car_Moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "危なかった……あとちょっとで……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "朝倉さん、ありがとうございます。\nすみません……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "あの……朝倉さん？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "行先のバーは第二象限にあるって、NEKOは言ってましたけど……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "道、分かりますか……？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos4503"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noahさん！？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aromaちゃん……やっと見つけたよ。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……私……！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あぁ！そんな怖がらないでくれ！\nこうするしか君とゆっくり話せる方法がなかったんだ……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ごめんね……全部僕のせいだ。\n君が逃げ出すのも仕方ない。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あの夜、僕とHelenaのケンカを……聞いてたんだろう？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……少しだけ……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "そうか……全部、君に話すよ。\n僕たちが……いや、僕が君にしたことを。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "全部……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "そうだ。\n全てを聞き終えたら、君は僕を恨むかもしれない。\nそれでもいいんだ……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……こうやって、僕たちは君を取り戻した。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "つまり、この身体は……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "そう、その身体は、もう君の物ではない。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……私……色んな……昔のお姉ちゃんとの思い出とか……思い出したのに……\n全部、全部……本物なのに……\nでも、時々矛盾するの……矛盾した景色を思い出すの……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "うん、それは、僕が今話したことが原因だ。\n理論上、今君の脳には2人分の記憶が入っていることになる……ごめん。\n本当にごめんね……僕を恨んでもらって構わないよ。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "ううん……私を助けたいって思ってくれた気持ちは分かる……だから……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "いや、待って。\nまだ話し終わってない……まだ……話すべきことがある。\nこれはHelenaも知らないことだ……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あの実験は、成功させられるものだったんだ。\nあれだけ失敗したのは……僕のせいだ。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "僕は、君の記憶に手を加えた。\n……あの夜のことを……思い出してほしくなかったから……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noahさんが酔っ払ってた時のことだよね？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……もう、思い出していたのか。\nそうだよ、僕はどんなに頑張っても、あの記憶のパラメーターをうまく調節することができなかった。\nだから、実験は失敗したんだ。\n全ては、僕の勝手な願いのせい。\nあれを思い出されてしまったら、もう二度と昔の楽しかったころには戻れないと思ったんだ……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あの時の自分は、そして、今これを君に話している自分は気持ち悪いと自分でも思うよ。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noahさんは、本当に私を「傷つける」行為はしてない。\nだって、酔っ払ってたNoahさんはすぐに眠ってしまったから……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "そんなことは関係ない……\nあの時、僕が君に抱いていた気持ちそのものが、抱くべきでなかったものなのだから。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……うん。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "今の僕はただ……君たち姉妹に幸せになって欲しいと願っているよ……\nこれは本当だ、本心だ……信じてほしい。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noahさん……私……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "着いたよ。\n中に入って話そう。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Car_Moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "好危險……差點就被……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "謝謝您，Asakura 先生，不好意思……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不過……Asakura 先生？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO 說，那間酒吧在第二象限……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "您……認得路吧？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos4503"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah！？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma……總算找到妳了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……我……！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳先別緊張！聽我說，只有這樣才有機會好好跟妳說……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "對不起……是我讓事情變成這樣的。妳會逃走，也是理所當然。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "那晚我跟妳姊姊吵架的對話……妳都聽見了吧？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……只聽到一點點……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "是嗎……那麼我現在要把一切都告訴妳。我們……不，我對妳做的一切。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "一切……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "沒錯，也許妳聽完後會恨我，那也沒關係……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……這就是我們將妳挽回的方式。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "所以這副身體……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "對，其實已經不是妳的身體了。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……我……對於已經想起的那些……跟姊姊小時候的記憶，的確都是真的。但是這中間又穿插著一些矛盾的畫面……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯，這就是原因。理論上妳現在的大腦存在著兩份記憶……對不起，想恨我也沒關係。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "我可以理解……你們想救我的心情，所以……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不，我還沒說完，我還有……還沒說完的事，連 Helena 也不知道的事……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "其實，這個實驗本來應該可以成功的，會失敗那麼多次……是因為我。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我對妳複製出來的記憶做了手腳，因為我那時一直不想讓妳想起……那一晚的事……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……Noah 喝醉那晚對我做的事對吧？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……原來妳也已經想起來了嗎？沒錯，我無論如何都無法把這些記憶參數控制在一個平衡點，才會導致一切都亂了套，因為我太害怕我們無法回到以前單純快樂的生活。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "對於變成那樣的自己，還有現在說著這些的自己，也感到噁心。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah 並沒有真的「傷害」到我，後來你就醉倒了……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "那不是重點……我當時對妳的感情，根本不該發生的。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我現在只希望妳們倆姊妹都幸福……這是真的，請相信我。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah……我……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "到家了，先進去再說吧。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Car_Moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "정말 위험했어요... 하마터면...\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "감사합니다, Asakura 씨. 그리고 죄송해요...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "저... Asakura 씨?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO가 그 술집은 2사분면에 있다고 했었는데...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "저... 길을 아세요...?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos4503"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah 씨!?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma... 드디어 찾았구나.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "...저는...!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "우선 긴장하지 말고 내 말 잘 들으렴. 이렇게라도 하지 않으면 네게 말할 기회가 없을 것 같아서...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "미안하구나... 전부 우리 때문에 일이 이렇게까지... 네가 도망치려 하는 것도 무리는 아니야.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그날 밤 나와 네 언니가 싸웠을 때... 전부 들었지?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "...조금...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그랬구나... 그렇다면 지금 전부 네게 말해줄게. 우리들이... 아니, 내가 네게 저질렀던 모든 일들을...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "모든... 일들...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그래. 다 듣고 나서 날 증오하게 된다고 해도 괜찮아...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......방금 말했던 것이 바로 우리가 너를 되돌리려던 방법이었단다.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "그래서 이 육체를...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그래. 사실 지금은 이미 네 몸이 아닌 게 돼버린 것 같지만.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "전... 이미 돌아온 기억들... 어렸을 때 언니와 함께 했던 기억들은... 전부 사실이었어요. 하지만 중간에 다른 어떤 모순된 화면이 겹치곤 했어요...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "응. 이게 바로 그 이유란다. 이론상으론 네 뇌에는 지금 두 개의 기억이 자리 잡고 있어... 미안하구나. 날 미워해도 괜찮아.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "이해해요... 당신들은... 절 구하고 싶은 마음에... 그래서...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아니. 아직 얘기 다 안 끝났어. 지금 하려는 얘기는... Helena조차도 모르는 일이야...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "사실... 이 실험은 충분히 성공시킬 수 있었음에도 그토록 실패했던 이유는... 바로 나 때문이란다.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "나는 복제한 네 기억을 건드렸어. 왜냐하면 네가 기억하고 있지 않기를 바랐거든... 그날 밤 일을...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "...Noah 씨가 술에 취해서 저질렀던... 그 일 말인가요?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "...이미 기억이 돌아왔나 보구나. 그래. 어떤 짓이든 다 해봤지만 그 일에 대한 기억 파라미터만큼은 제대로 조정할 수 없었어. 그래서 결국 모든 기억이 뒤죽박죽이 됐고 나는 우리가 옛날처럼 즐거웠던 시절로 돌아가지 못 할 수도 있을 거라는 불안감에 두려움이 커졌어.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그때의 내 모습... 그리고 지금 그 일을 네게 털어놓고 있는 나의 모습... 정말이지 역겹기 그지없어.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah 씨는 그때 정말로 제게 「상처」를 주려던 게 아니었어요. 혼자 취해서 넘어지고는...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "